message.body: Yeah, lots of driving today. How's your day?
Relatively good. I have to say, waking up in the a.m. feels good.
Nice nice. Going to able to sleep in the PM tonight?
I somehow doubt that. But I'm actually getting sleepy now, which is kind of ridiculous. How as Princeton?
It happened again! I fell asleep around nine something so I pretty much just has a whole night's sleep! So what am I going to do at 4 a.m.?
Aw man.... You gotta last until 11 and you'd be perfect.
I was pushing for at least midnight.
Lol. Either is good. But if you're tired at 9, 11 is good. Haha.
It's just weird hahah. How it going? Are you in Princeton or Bensalem today?
Princeton today. Got some issues to figure out...
Oh no, is everything okay?
I keep hearing rumors about bad moral and we have some housekeeping staffing issues.
Ohh good luck with that.
Yeah. Too many things to worry about.
Well it's almost the weekend :) you'll get through it. Go Steve!
I know. Need this weekend. Tired. Haha.
Going to be a chill weekend before you head out to Vegas again?
Nah, Vegas isnâ€™t until the next week
Oh cool, so you have some breathing room :)
Eh, don't need it. I like Vegas. Lol
Oh I see how it is hahah. Guess someone seems to be favoring the West Coast over the East Coast. Traitor!
Lol no no. Just Vegas.
Which is on the WEST Coast! Hahah. Did your mom enjoy her birthday?
She did. Got to gamble and shop. That's always good for her.
